{"tid":2442854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"揭沙頭角「愛國基地」涉退役解放軍 曾率白衣人圍《蘋果》 兼與何君堯合作","createTime":"2021-03-11T15:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T16:12:25.000Z","uid":126919,"like":100,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"da08a062773626993ef3a80911dd01a7921b391b","tid":2442854,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"在沙頭角出現的「愛國主義教育基地」，最近插上三支旗幟，除了五星紅旗，另外兩支均印有簡體字樣「致谢守卫者」的標誌。《蘋果》調查發現，標誌來自內地一個同名品牌，品牌由前駐港解放軍成員劉學創立，他近年活躍香港「藍絲」圈子，曾與「愛國主義教育基地」其中一名董事以「致谢守卫者」名義，拍住立法會議員何君堯舉辦愛國活動；又至少兩次在《蘋果》大樓外示威，前年更曾率眾到反修例示威現身，聲稱要「會一會」示威者。<br />\n<br />\n揭沙頭角「愛國基地」涉退役解放軍 曾率白衣人圍《蘋果》 兼與何君堯合作<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/CXWUKXULFREJLMP6SHLDWY5OCE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FCXWUKXULFREJLMP6SHLDWY5OCE%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHUngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=831b023b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FCXWUKXULFREJLMP6SHLDWY5OCE%2F&h=513d28af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/CXWUKXULFREJLMP6SHLDWY5OCE/</a>"},{"pid":"163ecd9d3d4a1a9ea5d0ed6a7e1245eae67d5524","tid":2442854,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ef1bba29319a62bf2f52fe5a997b6859c99f9d","tid":2442854,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"163ecd9d3d4a1a9ea5d0ed6a7e1245eae67d5524","tid":2442854,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"reply